docs {
  ## photo-feed API

  All requests use HttpOnly auth cookies — log in once via `auth/login` and the
  cookies stick for the rest of the requests in this run.

  Pick the `local` environment (top-right in Bruno UI) to use the seeded
  kyrylo@photo-feed.local / pass1234 against http://localhost:8000.
  `prod` is a template — fill `baseUrl`, `email`, and `password` per your deploy.
}
